ael) Cai, Director, Broadband & Gaming - Parks Associates<BR>Tim Harrison, Head of Games - Vodafone Group Services<BR>Guha Bala, President - Vicarious Visions, Inc.<BR>Greg Ballard, President and Chief Executive Officer - Glu Mobile<BR>John Koller, Senior Brand Manager, PSP - Sony Computer Entertainment America<BR>Karthik Bala, Chief Executive Officer - Vicarious Visions, Inc.<BR>Gonzague de Vallois, Vice President Publishing - Gameloft<BR>Matt Firor, Vice President of Development, Executive Producer - Mythic Entertainment<BR>Jason Williams, Marketing Director - GoGamer.com<BR>Kris Alexander, Sr. Product Manager, Digital Media & Gaming - Akamai<BR>Royal O'Brien, Founder and CEO - Game xStream<BR>Eric Hartness, Senior Director of Marketing - EA Nation - Electronic Arts<BR>Yoav Tzruya, Chief Operating Officer - Exent Technologies<BR>Jasper Smith, Director of Investigations - IPSA International, Inc.<BR>Mark Litvack, Partner - Mitchell, Silberberg & Krupp<BR>Andrew Myers, Special Agent - FBI - San Francisco, California<BR>Thomas Loeser, Assistant U.S. Attorney - U.S. Attorney's Office for the Central District of California<BR>Todd Hollenshead, CEO and Co-owner - id Software, Inc.<BR>Phil Terzian, Director, Government and Legislative Affairs - Activision, Inc.<BR></span></td>
